rame.svg](../../designs/issue-29/wireframe.svg)\n\n## 流程图\n\n```mermaid\nsequ
enceDiagram\n    participant U as 开发者\n    participant T as DevToolsToggleBut
ton\n    participant D as DevToolsDrawer\n    participant S as ServerUrlTool\n  
 participant C as DevToolsCubit\n    participant R as DevToolsRepository\n    pa
rticipant P as SharedPreferences\n    participant Dio as DioClient\n\n    U->>T:
点击悬浮按钮\n    T->>D: 触发 onToggle\n    D->>S: 展开抽屉，显示 URL 编辑卡片\n
   U->>S: 输入新的 Server Base URL\n    S->>C: onUrlChanged(url)\n    C->>C: 校
验 URL 格式\n    alt URL 格式非法\n        C-->>S: urlError = "请输入有效的 HTTP
/HTTPS URL"\n        S->>S: 输入框边框变红，保存按钮置灰\n    else URL 格式合法\
n        C-->>S: urlError = ""\n        S->>S: 保存按钮可用\n        U->>S: 点击
保存\n        S->>C: save()\n        C->>R: saveServerBaseUrl(url)\n        R->>
P: setString(\'dev_tools_server_base_url\', url)\n        P-->>R: 写入成功\n    
   R-->>C: 完成\n        C-->>S: saveSuccess = true\n        S->>Dio: 更新 baseU
rl\n        S->>S: 显示 SnackBar "保存成功，新配置已生效"\n    end\n```\n\n## 关
