ory 接口 | `apps/mobile/lib/domain/repositories/dev_tools_repository.dart` |\n| 
Repository 实现 | `apps/mobile/lib/data/repositories/dev_tools_repository_impl.d
art` |\n\n## 边界情况\n\n1. **Release 模式排除**：所有调试 Widget 必须包裹在 `if
